    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Angelbertus">Anghalperto</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>quondam <name ref="Ansualdus">Ansualdi</name></persName>
                        riceve da <persName ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>,
                        gratia Dei huius Sancte Lucane ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >episcopus</rs>, per cartula livellario nomine ad laborandum et
                        gubernanrdum seo meliorandum (…), casa et res illa in loco <placeName
                            ref="#places/357">Sugrominio</placeName>, quas antea <persName><name
                                ref="Liutbrandus">Liusprando</name></persName> ad manus suas abuit,
                        et ego ipsi modo exinde ad manus mea abere videor, pertenentes <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/70" key="#Churches">Sancti
                            Fridiani</orgName>, qui est de subpotestatem ecclesie <rs
                            key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> vestro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>; casa vero ipsa cum curte, orto, terris, ecc., olivis,
                        ecc. (…). Obbligo: in suprascripta casa resedere ecc., et tam ipsa casa quam
                        et res bene laborare ecc. (…). Censo: ad pars suprascripte eccl(esie) domus
                        epis(coporum) vestro Sancti Martini per sing(ulos) annos in ipso loco (…)
                        medietat(em) vinum purum, ad tertia vices uba ecc.; et (…) per sin(gulos)
                        annos medietat(em) oleo; et angaria vobis facere debeamus per sing(ulos)
                        annos per omnem ebdomatas dies duo, ubique vobis autilitas fuerit; et per
                        vindemia vos vel misso vestro super palmentum veneritis, nos vos recipere
                        ecc.; et a mandato vestro ecc. (…). Pena: argen(tum) solid(os) triginta
                            (…).<persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Teudimundus"
                                >Teudimundus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>. Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness"
                            >testimoni</rs>:<persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Allo"
                            >Aloni</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Allo"
                                >Aloni</name></persName> filio <persName>bone memorie <name
                                ref="Angelbertus">Angalperti</name></persName>, <persName
                            ref="#people/149" key="#Witness">Cunimundo</persName>, <persName
                            ref="#people/150" key="#Witness">Fraolmi</persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
